✦ Version v1.2.5: The Analytics & Optimization Update

This major update transforms Green Timer from a simple stopwatch into a powerful data-driven coding companion. We have completely overhauled the architecture to provide a lightning-fast, problem-centric experience.

🚀 NEW FEATURES:

1. Problem Deep Analytics (📊 Icon)
   * Dedicated Deep-Dive: Access a comprehensive performance modal for every problem.
   * Trend Visualization: Track your solving speed over time with beautiful Chart.js line graphs.
   * Advanced Metrics: Instant calculation of Average Speed, Personal Best, and Cumulative Time.
   * Attempt Timeline: A chronological log of every time you tackled a problem, including your saved notes and statuses.
   * Copy Report: Generate a professionally formatted Markdown report of your progress for your study notes.

2. Centralized Smart Tagging
   * Auto-Detection: Automatically captures LeetCode topic tags (Array, DP, String, etc.) as you browse.
   * Unified Sync: Tags are now centralized. Updating a tag on any attempt syncs it across your entire history for that problem.
   * Tag Manager: A new settings interface to manage your global tag library with usage counts.
   * Keyboard Autocomplete: A high-performance, keyboard-navigable menu for rapid tagging.

3. Advanced History Filtering
   * Multi-Select Filter: Filter your logs by multiple tags simultaneously using "AND" logic.
   * Removable Badges: Intuitive, high-contrast badges for managing active filters.
   * Quick Drill-Down: Click any tag in the Stats tab to instantly see all related problems in your history.

🏗️ ARCHITECTURAL EXCELLENCE:

* Problem-Centric Storage: Overhauled data structure to nested Problem/Submission objects, eliminating data redundancy and boosting performance.
* Live-Sync UI: Optimized internal loops (100ms) and refresh logic to ensure zero-flicker charts and live statistics.
* Theme-Aware Design: Fully optimized contrast for both Glass-Dark and Terminal-Light modes.
* Responsive Layout: Refactored unified two-row structure for perfect alignment on any screen size.

Everything is optimized. Everything is synchronized. Happy Coding!
